videos.headline: Ole Miss' Wilkins puts his team on the board
videos.description: RB Jordan Wilkins takes the pitch and turns on the jets for a 64-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Arkansas responds with a TD
videos.description: Colin Kelley completes a short screen pass to Devwah Whaley, who runs behind his lineman and into the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Rebels' Swinney gives his team the lead
videos.description: Eric Swinney takes the hand-off and runs it in for the touchdown .

videos.headline: Ole Miss offense looking explosive early
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu fires a pass to WR Damarkus Lodge for a big 44-yard gain.

videos.headline: Rebels' Ta'amu showing his versatility on TD
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu calls his own number on the QB keeper and races up the middle for a 49-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Rebels' WR Metcalf shows big play ability
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu completes a short pass to D.K. Metcalf and he breaks a tackle and runs up the sideline for a 31-yard scamper.

videos.headline: Ole Miss' Ta'amu scores his second TD of the day
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu takes the QB keeper eight yards into the end zone, giving him two touchdowns on the day.

videos.headline: Razorbacks continue to fight back
videos.description: QB Cole Kelley is pressured out of the pocket but makes a move on the defender and is able to score a tough 15-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Back-to-back turnovers give Arkansas life
videos.description: Ta'amu has his pass intercepted by Josh Lidell and he returns it 54-yards.

videos.headline: Arkansas cuts lead before halftime
videos.description: Cole Kelley completes the pass to Deon Stewart who scores an easy touchdown.

videos.headline: Ole Miss Coach Luke says they need to hold onto ball
videos.description: Interim coach Matt Luke says the Rebels haven't played bad they just need to hold onto the ball and limit the little mistakes.

videos.headline: Arkansas TD puts them within three
videos.description: Cole Kelley finds TE Cheyenne O' Grady on the screen pass and he takes it in from 9-yards out for the touchdown making the score 31-28.

videos.headline: Weird play leads to Arkansas turnover
videos.description: QB Cole Kelley is sacked by Marquis Haynes who forces the fumble, DeMarquis Gates recovers it barely after rolling to the ground. The play would be reviewed and Ole Miss would get the turnover.

videos.headline: Arkansas committs bad turnover
videos.description: On 4th down, Cole Kelley overthrows his receiver and is intercepted by Javien Hamilton who returns it 15-yards.

videos.headline: Ole Miss looks out of sorts on turnover
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu tries handing the ball off,  but fumbles in the process and CB Kevin Richardson returns it 22-yards for the defensive touchdown.

videos.headline: Arkansas completes crazy comeback with GW field goal
videos.description: Connor limpert nails a 34-yard field goal to give the Razorbacks the win.

videos.headline: Neal and Stinchcomb break down the final minutes of the game
videos.description: Matt Stinchcomb says "The story of the second half for Ole Miss is they were incapable of sustaining drives and getting it into the endzone."
